===================
TRON API for Python
===================

A Python API for interacting with the Tron (TRX)

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/tronapi.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/tronapi

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/tronapi.svg
